=== 耗資 ===
蘋果園區的土地成本估計為1.6億美元。2011年，蘋果園區前身Apple Campus 2的預算不足$30億美元<ref name="Burrows">{{cite web |last=Burrows |first=Peter |url=http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2013-04-04/apples-campus-2-shapes-up-as-an-investor-relations-nightmare |title=Inside Apple's Plans for Its Futuristic, $5 Billion Headquarters |work=Businessweek |access-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130529174905/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2013-04-04/apples-campus-2-shapes-up-as-an-investor-relations-nightmare |archive-date=2013-05-29 |url-status=live }}</ref>。然而，2013年的總成本估計接近$50億美元<ref name="Burrows" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2013/4/4/4182174/apple-campus-2-spaceship-overbudget-rumor|title=Apple Campus 2 nearly $2 billion over budget and behind schedule, says Bloomberg|website=The Verge|access-date=2016-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403194658/http://www.theverge.com/2013/4/4/4182174/apple-campus-2-spaceship-overbudget-rumor|archive-date=2016-04-03|url-status=live}}</ref>。

=== 能源供给 ===
蘋果園區是世界上最節能的建築之一<ref name="openingdate" />，主樓<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|date=2019-12-31|title=Apple Park Main Building|url=https://www.usgbc.org/projects/apple-park-main-building|access-date=2020-07-11|website=U.S. Green Building Council}}</ref>、史蒂夫·喬布斯劇院<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-12-31|title=Apple Park Steve Jobs Theatre|url=https://www.usgbc.org/projects/apple-park-steve-jobs-theatre|access-date=2020-07-11|website=U.S. Green Building Council}}</ref>與健身中心<ref>{{Cite web|date=2019-12-31|title=Apple Park Fitness Center|url=https://www.usgbc.org/projects/apple-park-fitness-center|access-date=2020-07-11|website=U.S. Green Building Council}}</ref>均獲得{{le|能源與環境設計領導|Leadership in Energy and Environmental Design}}的白金認證<ref name="#1"/>。在2018年4月的新聞稿中，蘋果公司宣布它已轉為完全由[[可再生能源|可再生能源]]供電<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2018/04/apple-now-globally-powered-by-100-percent-renewable-energy/|title=Apple now globally powered by 100 percent renewable energy|website=Apple Newsroom|language=en-US|access-date=2019-11-04}}</ref>。安裝在園區屋頂上的太陽能電池板在每天的日照時間下可產生17兆瓦的電力，足以在白天高峰時段提供75%的電力<ref name="CupertinoCityCouncil">{{cite web|url=http://www.cupertino.org/index.aspx?recordid=463&page=410|title=Cupertino : City News : Steve Jobs Presents to Cupertino City Council|publisher=Cupertino City Council|access-date=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609230452/http://www.cupertino.org/index.aspx?recordid=463&page=410|archive-date=2016-06-09|url-status=live}}</ref>，並使其成為{{le|世界上最大的太陽能屋頂之一|List of rooftop photovoltaic installations#In operation 2}}。其餘在現場利用{{le|布鲁姆能源伺服器|Bloom Energy Server}}的[[燃料電池|燃料電池]]產生的4兆瓦的電力，那是由[[生物燃料|生物燃料]]和[[天然氣|天然氣]]驅動<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/06/24/apples-campus-2-to-use-updated-bloom-energy-fuel-cells-first-deployed-at-nc-data-center|title=Apple's Campus 2 to use updated Bloom Energy fuel cells first deployed at NC data center|publisher=Apple Insider|access-date=2016-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630012133/http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/06/24/apples-campus-2-to-use-updated-bloom-energy-fuel-cells-first-deployed-at-nc-data-center|archive-date=2016-06-30|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/06/24/apples-campus-2-to-use-updated-bloom-energy-fuel-cells-first-deployed-at-nc-data-center|title=Apple's Campus 2 to use updated Bloom Energy fuel cells first deployed at NC data center|publisher=|accessdate=2017-06-02|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630012133/http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/06/24/apples-campus-2-to-use-updated-bloom-energy-fuel-cells-first-deployed-at-nc-data-center|dead-url=no}}</ref>。空氣能夠於建築物的內外之間自由流動，提供自然通風環境，並且在一年中的九個月內不需要使用[[暖通空調|暖通空調]]系統<ref name="openingdate" />。

== 設施 ==
=== 咖啡店 ===
園區內有七家咖啡店，最大的是一家三層咖啡店，可容納3,000人就座。它以淺色的石材襯裡沒有金屬支撐的玻璃欄杆，周圍以廣泛的園林綠化環繞著。{{convert|20,000|sqft|m2|abbr=on}}的[[夾層|夾層]]空間可容納600人，室外露台設有1,750個座位，那裡有由專門設計的500張[[施佩薩爾特|施佩薩爾特]]實心白橡木製成的餐桌，其大小為長{{convert|18|ft|m|abbr=on}}，寬{{convert|4|ft|m|abbr=on}}。該咖啡店每天可供應15,000份午餐。

運動桌和長凳的款式類似於[[Apple_Store|Apple Store]]的那些。

=== 禮堂 ===
[[File:Steve_Jobs_Theater_-_external.jpg|thumb]]
禮堂的建築物位於園區一座小山丘的建築物內，它於北丹陶大道（North Tantau Avenue）有350個停車位，還有一條通往禮堂西北部主園區的行人道。禮堂建築物有一個大型地上圓柱形大堂，大堂採用圓柱形玻璃牆，沒有支撐柱，提供園區360°無阻礙的全景視野。樓梯向下通往禮堂。該禮堂的名稱以蘋果公司[[組織創始人|聯合創始人]]兼前[[首席执行官|行政總裁]][[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史提夫·喬布斯]]來命名<ref name="openingdate" />，該地下的禮堂有1,000個座位，用於蘋果公司的產品發布和舉行新聞發布會。

禮堂建築物的屋頂由44塊相同的{{convert|80|ST|t|abbr=off|sp=us|adj=on}}[[碳纖維強化聚合物|碳纖維]]面板組成，由迪拜公司Premier Composite Technologies提供。每塊面板長{{convert|70|ft|m|abbr=on}}，寬{{convert|11|ft|m|abbr=on}}，並與其他面板鎖定在中間<ref>{{cite web|url=http://qz.com/699112/what-apple-is-building-wwdc/|title=What is Apple actually doing besides building that ridiculously expensive new headquarters?|first=Mike|last=Murphy|access-date=2016-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625120550/http://qz.com/699112/what-apple-is-building-wwdc/|archive-date=2016-06-25|url-status=live}}</ref>。它是世界上最大的碳纖維屋頂和玻璃支撐結構<ref name=foster />。禮堂建築物還包括一個{{convert|42|ft|adj=on}}高的玻璃電梯，能夠從建築物底部旋轉171°至上層大堂。電梯由化學鋼化玻璃製成，那被認為是世界上最高的獨立式玻璃電梯<ref name=foster>{{cite web|url=https://www.fosterandpartners.com/news/archive/2017/09/the-steve-jobs-theater-at-apple-park/|title=The Steve Jobs Theater at Apple Park – Foster + Partners|first=Foster + Partners /|last=www.fosterandpartners.com|website=www.fosterandpartners.com|access-date=2017-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009234803/https://www.fosterandpartners.com/news/archive/2017/09/the-steve-jobs-theater-at-apple-park/|archive-date=2017-10-09|url-status=live}}</ref>。

禮堂舉行的首場發布會於2017年9月12日舉行，在那裡發布了[[iPhone_8|iPhone 8、iPhone 8 Plus]]、[[iPhone_X|iPhone X]]、[[Apple_Watch_Series_3|Apple Watch Series 3]]和[[Apple_TV_4K|Apple TV 4K]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/8/31/16233998/apple-iphone-8-event-september-12th-invitation|title=Apple's iPhone 8 event is happening on September 12th|work=The Verge|access-date=2017-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831183143/https://www.theverge.com/2017/8/31/16233998/apple-iphone-8-event-september-12th-invitation|archive-date=2017-08-31|url-status=live}}</ref>。

{{wide image|Steve Jobs Theater - Auditorium.jpg|800px|位於加州庫比蒂諾蘋果園區內的史蒂夫喬布斯劇院禮堂全景圖。照片攝於在劇院舉行的蘋果公司首次股東大會。}}

=== 健身中心 ===
佔地{{convert|100,000|sqft|m2|adj=on}}的[[健身中心|健身中心]]位於園區的西北方，除了[[健身器材|健身器材]]外，健身中心還提供其他設施，如[[更衣室|更衣室]]、[[淋浴間|淋浴間]]、洗衣服務和小組會議室<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/news/2018/02/27/apple-offers-new-wellness-program-headquarters-employees/377609002/|title=Apple offers new wellness program for headquarters employees|last=Cava|first=Marco della|website=USA TODAY|language=en-US|access-date=2020-02-16}}</ref>。

=== 研發設施 ===
[[研究開發|研究開發]]設施包括位於園區南端的兩座{{convert|300,000|sqft|m2}}的大型建築，可容納2,000多人。每棟建築的頂層都設有由工業設計和人類界面團隊組成的部門，該團隊之前由首席設計師[[乔纳森·艾维|莊拿芬·伊夫]]領導<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://appleinsider.com/articles/17/03/24/new-apple-park-drone-footage-reveals-occupied-research-and-development-building-landscaping-progress|title=New Apple Park drone footage reveals occupied research and development building, landscaping progress|last1=Friday|first1=Mike Wuerthele|last2=March 24|website=AppleInsider|language=en|access-date=2020-02-16|last3=2017|last4=PT|first4=01:29 pm}}</ref>。

=== 護理診所 ===
近年來，蘋果公司開始於聖克拉拉縣開設護理診所，以在該公司的工作場所提供無障礙的醫療保健和促進健康行為。這構想把醫療保健帶入社區增強了包容性，並為大多數公司的傳統醫療保健選擇帶來了實際變化<ref>{{Cite web|title=Apple is launching medical clinics to deliver the 'world's best health care experience' to its employees|url=https://www.cnbc.com/2018/02/27/apple-launching-medical-clinics-for-employees.html|last=Farr|first=Christina|date=2018-02-27|website=CNBC|language=en|access-date=2020-05-08}}</ref>。

=== 交通 ===
==== 巴士 ====
乘坐巴士往返的員工將在巴士車站上下車，車站通過兩道白色樓梯通往主園區。{{le|聖克拉拉谷交通管理局（VTA）|Santa Clara Valley Transportation Authority}}也為該範圍提供服務，該機構經營從庫比蒂諾到附近城市的當地巴士服務。跟VTA合作為園區提供服務的著名交通顧問{{le|賈勒特·沃克|Jarrett Walker}}由於使用公共交通上的不便而批評園區的設計<ref>{{Cite web|last=Brinklow|first=Adam|date=2017-04-27|title=Tech companies should move closer to transit, says new report|url=https://sf.curbed.com/2017/4/27/15458764/spur-silicon-valley-transit-report-sf|access-date=2020-12-11|website=Curbed SF|language=en}}</ref>。

==== 汽車 ====
[[停車場|停車場]]位於地下和兩個可容納約14,200名員工的大型停車場<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.co.uk/feature/apple/apple-spaceship-campus-facts-pictures-video-info-video-3489704|title=Apple sends out photos of near-complete Campus 2 HQ ahead of 2017 launch|first=Amy|last=Moore|publisher=Macworld|access-date=2016-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623051436/http://www.macworld.co.uk/feature/apple/apple-spaceship-campus-facts-pictures-video-info-video-3489704/|archive-date=2016-06-23|url-status=live}}</ref>。庫比蒂諾法規要求至少有11,000個停車位<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.nl/apple-park-new-campus-more-parking-than-offices-2017-4/?international=true&r=US|title=Apple's new $5 billion campus has more space for parking than offices|first=Kif|last=Leswing|date=2017-04-09|work=BusinessInsider|access-date=2017-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418081900/https://www.businessinsider.nl/apple-park-new-campus-more-parking-than-offices-2017-4/?international=true&r=US|archive-date=2017-04-18|url-status=live}}</ref>，當中700個設有[[電動汽車|電動汽車]][[充电桩|充电桩]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Environmental Responsibility Report|url=https://images.apple.com/environment/pdf/Apple_Environmental_Responsibility_Report_2017.pdf|publisher=Apple Inc.|date=2017|access-date=2017-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170421013446/https://images.apple.com/environment/pdf/Apple_Environmental_Responsibility_Report_2017.pdf|archive-date=2017-04-21|url-status=live}}</ref>。

[[地下停車場|地下停車場]]設有2,000個停車位，由管理交通和停車位的傳感器和應用程式管理<ref name="MC-parking">{{cite web|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/2017/02/24/apple-campus-city-public-works-shares-insights-into-traffic-sheer-size-of-project|title=Apple Park: Cupertino shares insights into traffic, sheer size of project|first=Kristi|last=Myllenbeck|date=2017-02-24|work=The Mercury News|access-date=2017-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170418081804/http://www.mercurynews.com/2017/02/24/apple-campus-city-public-works-shares-insights-into-traffic-sheer-size-of-project/|archive-date=2017-04-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。

==== 單車 ====
園區內有1,000輛單車供員工四處走走，在佔地{{convert|175|acre|ha|adj=on}}的園區內擁有數英里的單車徑道和慢跑徑道<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/apple-designed-bikes-new-campus-created-by-public-bikes-photos-2018-1|title=Check out the beautifully minimalist bikes Apple designed for its $5 billion campus|last=Leswing|first=Kif|website=Business Insider|access-date=2019-11-04}}</ref>。地下停車場還有2,000個額外的單車停泊位<ref name="MC-parking" />。

=== 访客中心 ===
{{main|Apple Park 访客中心}}
[[File:Apple_Park_-_Visitor_Center_-_Side_view_-_November_2017.jpg|thumb]]
蘋果園區外設置了獨立的訪客中心供訪客了解園區的建築，那是一座{{convert|20,135|sqft|m2|adj=on}}的兩層樓高建築，它有四個主要區域：
* [[Apple_Store|Apple Store]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://news.fastcompany.com/here-are-all-the-details-on-apple-park-the-companys-massive-new-spaceship-campus-4031078|title=Here are all the details on Apple Park, the company's massive new spaceship campus|work=Fast Company|date=2017-02-22|access-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225142736/https://news.fastcompany.com/here-are-all-the-details-on-apple-park-the-companys-massive-new-spaceship-campus-4031078|archive-date=2017-02-25|url-status=live}}</ref>，該店銷售其品牌的紀念商品並不會於一般蘋果商店出售（如T恤、帽子、手提包、明信片）<ref>{{cite web|title=Apple Park Visitor Center Set to Open by Year's End (Byways Magazine)|url=https://apple.news/Avw0kKJh4S_ebSasCZDNaUA|website=Byways|access-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102004444/https://apple.news/Avw0kKJh4S_ebSasCZDNaUA|archive-date=2017-11-02|url-status=live}}</ref>，但並不會有「Today at Apple」活動或提供Genius Bar服務；
* 一家{{convert|2,386|sqft|m2|adj=on}}的咖啡廳；
* 一個展覽空間，目前展示了具有[[擴增實境|擴增實境]]功能（AR技術）的蘋果園區3D模型，以及
* 一個俯瞰園區的屋頂露台。

它於2017年11月17日向公眾開放<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hein|first1=Buster|title=Apple Park visitor center opens doors to the public {{!}} Cult of Mac|url=https://www.cultofmac.com/514753/apple-park-visitor-center-opens-doors-public/|website=Cult of Mac|access-date=2017-11-17|date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171118033125/https://www.cultofmac.com/514753/apple-park-visitor-center-opens-doors-public/|archive-date=2017-11-18|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Wuerthele|first1=Mike|title=Apple Park visitors center complete, slated to open before end of 2017|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/17/10/30/apple-park-visitors-center-complete-slated-to-open-before-end-of-2017|website=AppleInsider|access-date=2017-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171031081306/http://appleinsider.com/articles/17/10/30/apple-park-visitors-center-complete-slated-to-open-before-end-of-2017|archive-date=2017-10-31|url-status=live}}</ref>。該中心的估計成本為$8,000萬美元<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/01/18/apple-to-spend-80m-on-campus-2-visitor-center|title=Apple to spend $80M on Campus 2 visitor center|first=Mikey|last=Campbell|date=2016-01-18|work=AppleInsider|access-date=2017-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218143500/http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/01/18/apple-to-spend-80m-on-campus-2-visitor-center|archive-date=2017-02-18|url-status=live}}</ref>。該物業位於坦陶的10600 N（坦陶與普魯內里奇的東北角），在園區對面馬路的對面，毗鄰聖克拉拉住宅區<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fortune.com/2015/07/30/apple-visitors-center-spaceship|title=Apple visitor's center will offer views of Steve Jobs' Spaceship|first=Philip|last=Elmer-DeWitt|date=2015-07-30|work=Fortune|access-date=2017-02-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228043515/http://fortune.com/2015/07/30/apple-visitors-center-spaceship/|archive-date=2017-02-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。其地下停車場擁有近700個車位，估計耗資$2,600萬美元。訪客中心是園區訪客唯一允許參觀的部分。

== 地面 ==
=== 園林綠化 ===
[[File:Apple_Campus_2_Jan16.jpg|thumb]]
園區的80%由綠地組成<ref name="APark jobs council">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=06QqipaAvGY|title=Steve Jobs TV Appearance at the Cupertino City Council (6/7/11)|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2011-07-06|access-date=2017-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629130329/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=06QqipaAvGY|archive-date=2016-06-29|url-status=live}}</ref>，主樓中間寬敞的庭院種植了杏、橄欖和蘋果園，以及咖啡店附近的藥草園。為了園區的園林綠化而選擇的其他植物都是耐旱的，園區使用再生水來澆灌植物。

2010年，喬布斯得知{{le|史丹福盤|Stanford Dish}}附近橡樹的質量後，他要求工作人員尋覓照顧它們的[[樹藝師|樹藝師]]<ref name="Levy" />。蘋果公司於2011年聘得樹藝師戴夫·馬弗利（Dave Muffly）為蘋果園區附近培育加州自然環境<ref name="Levy">{{cite news|last1=Levy|first1=Steven|author-link1=Steven Levy|title=Apple Park's Tree Whisperer|url=https://www.wired.com/story/apple-parks-tree-whisperer/|access-date=2018-03-19|work=Wired|publisher=Condé Nast|date=2017-06-01|location=San Francisco|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180319213741/https://www.wired.com/story/apple-parks-tree-whisperer/|archive-date=2018-03-19|url-status=live}}</ref>。蘋果園區內有9,000棵樹，其中有309個品種為本土樹種<ref name="openingdate" /><ref name=VBtree />。種植的樹木有{{le|橡樹稀樹草原|Oak savanna}}、[[櫟屬|橡木]]和一些果樹，包括[[杏組|杏]]、蘋果、梅子、櫻桃和[[柿|柿]]子。額外的{{convert|15|acre|0}}土地用作[[草原|加州本土草原]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cnga.org/page-1633090|title=California Native Grasslands Association – Grass Facts|access-date=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809200925/http://www.cnga.org/page-1633090|archive-date=2016-08-09|url-status=live}}</ref>。蘋果品種的代表包括{{le|金冠蘋果|Golden Delicious}}、[[澳洲青蘋|翠玉蘋果]]、{{le|格拉文斯頓蘋果|Gravenstein}}及{{le|秋蜜蘋果|Cripps Pink}}，但值得注意的是[[旭蘋果|旭蘋果]]卻不在列<ref name="Levy" />。

在馬弗利開始認真工作後，他意識到4,000棵現有的樹木中可用的不足100棵<ref name="Levy" />。這意味著他不得不從頭開始採購幾乎所有計劃中的9,000棵樹<ref name="Levy" />。他的團隊甚至去尋找棄置的{{le|聖誕樹種植農場|Christmas tree cultivation}}，而蘋果公司於[[莫哈韋沙漠|莫哈韋沙漠]]的[[耶莫_(加利福尼亞州)|耶莫]]收購了一個<ref name="Levy" />。

=== 歷史穀倉 ===
[[File:Glendenning_Barn_1.jpg|thumb]]
蘋果公司為園區所購得的土地包括著一個由約翰·倫納德（John Leonard）於1916年使用紅木板建造的舊[[穀倉|穀倉]]，倫納德與格倫登寧家族結婚，格倫登寧家族於1850年代從蘇格蘭移民至美國並在該地定居。蘋果公司購得該處房產後，他們與庫比蒂諾歷史協會和庫比蒂諾市之間就著穀倉的命運進行了討論。該城市對穀倉的興趣源於其在2004年宣佈為歷史遺址<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/2017/07/14/barn-at-apple-park-represents-hard-work-of-generations-of-visionaries/|title=Barn at Apple Park represents 'hard work' of generations of 'visionaries'|date=2017-07-14|work=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]]|access-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719185000/http://www.mercurynews.com/2017/07/14/barn-at-apple-park-represents-hard-work-of-generations-of-visionaries/|archive-date=2017-07-19|url-status=live}}</ref>。

最終，蘋果公司同意把穀倉保留於該物業上，並用它作為「存放維護工具和其他景觀物料」。該穀倉於園區建設期間被拆除，然後在跟它原先不同的位置重新組裝<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.macrumors.com/2017/07/13/apple-park-july-2017-drone-video|title=Apple Has Finished Moving and Precisely Reassembling a Historic Barn At Its New Headquarters|date=2017-07-13|first=Joe|last=Rossignol|access-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170715144303/https://www.macrumors.com/2017/07/13/apple-park-july-2017-drone-video/|archive-date=2017-07-15|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mercurynews.com/2017/07/14/barn-at-apple-park-represents-hard-work-of-generations-of-visionaries|title=Barn at Apple Park represents 'hard work' of generations of 'visionaries'|date=2017-07-14|first=Kristi|last=Myllenbeck|work=[[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]]|access-date=2017-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170719185000/http://www.mercurynews.com/2017/07/14/barn-at-apple-park-represents-hard-work-of-generations-of-visionaries/|archive-date=2017-07-19|url-status=live}}</ref>。

=== 內庭院 ===
內部庭院佔地{{convert|30|acre|ha}}，在人工池塘和咖啡店旁種滿了果樹。內裡有著幾個拱門的一個長方形場地在中央，從遠處看就像[[彩虹|彩虹]]一樣。

== 批評 ==
隨著蘋果公司尋求遷至擁有交通便利、單車和行人通道更方便的城市地區，園區的設計被稱為郊區辦公園區的「終極例子」<ref>{{cite news |last=Goodyear |first=Sarah |date=2011-06-14 |title=As suburban office parks lose steam, Apple unveils the ultimate example |url=http://grist.org/sprawl/2011-06-14-as-suburban-office-parks-lose-steam-apple-unveils-the-ultimate-e/ |work=[[Grist_(magazine)|Grist]] |access-date=2017-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206140029/http://grist.org/sprawl/2011-06-14-as-suburban-office-parks-lose-steam-apple-unveils-the-ultimate-e/ |archive-date=2017-12-06 |url-status=live }}</ref>。一個非盈利環保組織{{le|自然資源保護委員會|Natural Resources Defense Council}}的凱德·本菲爾德（Kaid Benfield）批評擬議的園區對現有[[城市蔓延|城市蔓延]]作出的貢獻，具有依賴汽車的功能和浪費本可以用於{{le|經濟房屋|Affordable housing}}的昂貴房地產<ref>{{cite news |last=Benfield |first=Kaid |date=2012-03-13 |title=If you care about cities, return that new iPad |publisher=[[Natural_Resources_Defense_Council|Natural Resources Defense Council]] |url=http://switchboard.nrdc.org/blogs/kbenfield/if_you_care_about_cities_retur.html |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120504000649/http://switchboard.nrdc.org/blogs/kbenfield/if_you_care_about_cities_retur.html |archive-date=2012-05-04 |access-date=2017-12-04 }}</ref>。

2018年有消息稱，有兩名工人在走進大樓的透明玻璃牆和門時受傷並需要住院治療，總部也因此受到不利的關注<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.marketwatch.com/story/people-are-walking-into-glass-at-the-new-apple-headquarters-2018-02-15 |title=Archived copy |access-date=2018-03-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180313094212/https://www.marketwatch.com/story/people-are-walking-into-glass-at-the-new-apple-headquarters-2018-02-15 |archive-date=2018-03-13 |url-status=live }}</ref>。

蘋果公司因其新總部的奢侈以及其設計和建造的完美主義而受到一些批評。據報導，使用特殊木材作為建築材料是其30頁指南的主題<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-apple-campus-idUSKBN15M0CM|title=Channeling Steve Jobs, Apple seeks design perfection at new...|last=Love|first=Julia|work=U.S.|access-date=2018-05-28|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515175005/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-apple-campus-idUSKBN15M0CM|archive-date=2017-05-15|url-status=live}}</ref>。門把手的設計據報是為期一年半辯論的主題，在蘋果公司管理層批准之前涉及多次修訂<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.techtimes.com/articles/196461/20170208/apple-repeated-delays-to-perfect-spaceship-campus-reveal-why-it-is-extravagantly-anti-people.htm|title=Apple Repeated Delays To Perfect Spaceship Campus Reveal Why It Is Extravagantly Anti-People|last=Loterina|first=Chris|date=2017-02-08|work=Tech Times|access-date=2018-05-28|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528133644/http://www.techtimes.com/articles/196461/20170208/apple-repeated-delays-to-perfect-spaceship-campus-reveal-why-it-is-extravagantly-anti-people.htm|archive-date=2018-05-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。蘋果公司對定制標牌的渴望使公司跟聖克拉拉縣消防局產生了分歧，由於擔心在緊急情況下會危及安全，因此需要進行多輪談判<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.siliconbeat.com/2017/02/07/apples-spaceship-campus-more-than-a-year-to-approve-a-door-handle-report-says/|title=Apple's 'spaceship' campus: more than a year to approve a door handle, and toilets like iPhones, report says|date=2017-02-07|work=SiliconBeat|access-date=2018-05-28|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180528220229/http://www.siliconbeat.com/2017/02/07/apples-spaceship-campus-more-than-a-year-to-approve-a-door-handle-report-says/|archive-date=2018-05-28|url-status=live}}</ref>。

由作者{{le|張秀春|Emily Chang (journalist)}}在她的著作《{{le|布羅托邦|Brotopia}}》一書中批評儘管蘋果園區表面上是服務於每個人的需求，然而它沒有為員工的孩子提供日間托管的設施<ref>{{cite book |last=Chang|first=Emily|author-link=Emily Chang (journalist)|date=2018-02-06|title=[[Brotopia|Brotopia: Breaking Up the Boys' Club of Silicon Valley]]|publisher=Portfolio|isbn=978-0-7352-1353-1}}</ref>。

